{"tid":1763009,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"光復香港教育制度","createTime":"2019-11-30T04:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T16:20:32.000Z","uid":205482,"like":35,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"eed4b3300ef08c7111265f10e3c1ddd4ef4f39a7","tid":1763009,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"主意：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永久廢除中文中學，將母語授課改為英語授課。全港中學生使用英文教科書以及英文試卷為最低限度。（唔計中文科）<br />\n<br />\n2. 強烈建議電腦科老師教授小學生以及初中生倉頡同速成輸入法、至少20%常用功能同應用嘅Microsoft Word, PowerPoint, Excel 同 Adobe Photoshop<br />\n<br />\n3. 中學老師同前輩請多鼓勵學生重視身高問題，尤其係踏入青春期嘅初中生。<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n<br />\n1. 無差別提升全港青少年嘅英文水平，並視之為基本同輕易掌握嘅終生實用技能。即使非大專生，只有中學學歷嘅市民都熟悉國際語言。差極都有個譜<br />\n<br />\n2. 全面增強青少年嘅硬同軟技能，軟技能包括溝通能力 （口語及文字）、 說服力、創意、解難能力、團隊合作能力、適應能力、正面思考、從批判中學習同埋時間管理。加強香港人喺職場上嘅競爭優勢。<br />\n<br />\n3. 最後，不解釋<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/zcTgyTF.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzcTgyTF.gif&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf3PcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=96e9ea75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/zcTgyTF.gif</a>"},{"pid":"10e563e012f8493e013f65dffef1ce53cebac0b5","tid":1763009,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:00:34.000Z","msg":"相關資訊：<br />\n<br />\n隨住科技發展，好多現時靠人手做嘅嘢，以 Hard Skills 為主導嘅工作將會被自動化 (Automation）同人工智能 （Artificial Intelligence）取代，所以將來嘅工種將會更依賴 Soft Skills。<br />\n<br />\nDeloitte Access Economics 今年發佈嘅研究就指出，以澳洲為例，估計到 2030年整個市場就會有七成工種係以 Soft Skills 主導。而呢個趨勢亦勢必會係全球擴展。<br />\n<br />\nSources: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.jobable.com/blog-zh/amp/soft-skill-%25E5%25AE%259A-hard-skill-%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25EF%25BC%259F%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E8%25B3%259E%25E8%25AD%2598%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25BE%2580%25E5%25BE%2580%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2582%25A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.jobable.com%2Fblog-zh%2Famp%2Fsoft-skill-%2525E5%2525AE%25259A-hard-skill-%2525E9%252587%25258D%2525E8%2525A6%252581%2525EF%2525BC%25259F%2525E8%252580%252581%2525E9%252597%252586%2525E8%2525B3%25259E%2525E8%2525AD%252598%2525E7%25259A%252584%2525E5%2525BE%252580%2525E5%2525BE%252580%2525E4%2525B8%25258D%2525E6%252598%2525AF%2525E8%2525BE%2525A6%2525E4%2525BA%25258B%2525E8%252583%2525BD%2525E5%25258A%25259B%2525E9%2525AB%252598%2525E9%252582%2525A3%2F&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf3PcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=d8e0e9ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.jobable.com/blog-zh/amp/soft-skill-%25E5%25AE%259A-hard-skill-%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25EF%25BC%259F%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E8%25B3%259E%25E8%25AD%2598%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25BE%2580%25E5%25BE%2580%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2582%25A3/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.deloitte.com/au/en/pages/economics/articles/soft-skills-business-success.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fau%2Fen%2Fpages%2Feconomics%2Farticles%2Fsoft-skills-business-success.html&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf3PcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=bc8872f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.deloitte.com/au/en/pages/economics/articles/soft-skills-business-success.html</a>"},{"pid":"321c4b98f2f81a9dc3a2fd614fe0ef3387805b65","tid":1763009,"uid":135408,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"光復AL得唔得"},{"pid":"29f646bde8152b1deb5bedcd435ac58b76242e34","tid":1763009,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6c64b6e6efdefc33edc6f75277ec56ccbe9361","tid":1763009,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl